Maximun 7 big works and possibly some smaller drawings as well, I guess I will discuss it with Jan later, I'm happy to take feedback from you guys as well!

A party after the vernissage would be great, its a perfect place for a ~corona safe~ party anyway, and people are already used to things happening there on fridays anyway. So yeah, if some of you would like to help me with the party as well that would be great :))))

@hampus @hugi @sofia @Linnea @bob @Lekonst @NinaLindberg

